# VibeChess API Tests

### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new game
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/games
Accept: application/json

###

### Submit white prompt (replace GAME_CODE with actual code)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/games/GAME_CODE/prompt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "color": "white",
  "prompt": "Play aggressively, go for quick attacks and control the center"
}

###

### Submit black prompt (replace GAME_CODE with actual code)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/games/GAME_CODE/prompt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "color": "black",
  "prompt": "Play defensively, protect the king and build a solid position"
}

###

### Get game state (replace GAME_CODE with actual code)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/games/GAME_CODE
Accept: application/json

###

### Subscribe to game events (SSE) - replace GAME_CODE
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/games/GAME_CODE/events
Accept: text/event-stream

